Text: MSCF Advisory Board MeetingAll You are invited to attend the next Advisory Group meeting for Carnegie Mellons Computational Finance Program It will be held on December at the Club QuartersMidtown located at West th Street The schedule is as follows Cocktails pm Dinner pm If you need a room reserved please let us know and arrangements will be made If you have any questions please feel free to contact me or Norene Mears at Sincerely Sue Connelly Administrative Coordinator MS in Computational Finance Program Graduate School of Industrial Administration Carnegie Mellon University
